          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Rhinebeck sits in the heart of the Hudson Valley — surrounded by farm stands, hiking trails, antique shops, and some of the best food in New York State. Whether you come for a weekend or a week, there is always something worth discovering.</p>",
